SHE IS NOT
AN ILL HOSPITAL PATIENT.

00:03:03,550 --> 00:03:06,319
SHE IS A BEAUTIFUL,
PREGNANT MOTHER,

00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:08,822
AND WHAT SHE'S WEARING
SHOULD REFLECT THAT JOY,

00:03:08,822 --> 00:03:11,558
AND THAT'S PRECISELY WHY
I DESIGNED HOT MAMA GOWNS.

00:03:11,558 --> 00:03:14,161
NOW GIVE ME YOUR MONEY, OKAY?
(chuckles)

