AND RESPECT IT.

00:05:49,115 --> 00:05:52,519
NOBODY KNOWS WHO YOU ARE,
DEIDREA.
HOW DO YOU KNOW? THEY DO.

00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:55,255
YOU'RE DOING $11,000 A YEAR
IN SALES.
THIS IS BRAND‐NEW.

