PAST. I NEED MORE INVENTORY.

00:06:02,796 --> 00:06:04,798
SO THE NEXT TIME I GO
TO MY MANUFACTURER,

00:06:04,798 --> 00:06:07,367
I'M GOING WITH BIGGER NUMBERS,
'CAUSE NOW I HAVE MONEY,

00:06:07,367 --> 00:06:09,402
