ONE HELL OF A LONG ROAD.
I DON'T AGREE.

00:07:17,837 --> 00:07:20,473
I DON'T WANT TO TAKE THAT ROAD.

00:07:20,473 --> 00:07:23,510
I DON'T WANT TO RIDE THAT ROAD
WITH YOU. I'M SORRY.
IT'S A GOOD ROAD.

00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:26,146
(O'Leary) IT'S A LONG ROAD.
