WOMAN‐‐THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

00:07:56,576 --> 00:07:58,078
HAVE YOU EVER CONSIDERED

00:07:58,078 --> 00:08:00,981
LICENSING THIS IDEA
TO THE GOWN COMPANIES?

00:08:00,981 --> 00:08:03,049
