WANT A ONE‐SIZE‐FITS‐ALL GOWN.
HERE'S THE ISSUE‐‐YOU KNOW,

00:08:09,289 --> 00:08:11,291
IT'S WHAT YOU THINK
THAT YOU ALREADY KNOW

00:08:11,291 --> 00:08:14,894
THAT WILL PREVENT YOU
FROM LEARNING.
IT'S TOO HIGH‐END.

00:08:14,894 --> 00:08:17,263
