00:40:33,196 --> 00:40:35,865
TWO GUYS WANT TO MAKE MONEY.
I UNDERSTAND THAT.

00:40:35,865 --> 00:40:39,135
SHANE, SHANE, YOU KNOW WHAT? WE
UNDERSTAND PRODUCT, AND WE WILL

00:40:39,135 --> 00:40:42,138
GET ALSO LICENSING ONCE
WE GET TO A COMFORTABLE LEVEL.

00:40:42,138 --> 00:40:46,008
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO?
LET'S DO SOMETHING.
$80,000
FOR 25% OF THE COMPANY?

00:40:46,008 --> 00:40:48,644
CORRECT.
$80,000, 25% OF THE COMPANY.

00:40:48,644 --> 00:40:51,848
HE DOES THE INFOMERCIALS,
I DO PRODUCT TO STORES,

00:40:51,848 --> 00:40:56,586
WE HELP BUILD A BRAND ITSELF.

00:40:56,586 --> 00:41:01,324
SHANE, I WANT‐‐
I WANT AN ANSWER.
I'M GONNA CALL MY WIFE.

00:41:01,324 --> 00:41:03,826
I WANT TO TALK TO YOUR WIFE.
YOU WANT TO TALK TO MY WIFE?

00:41:03,826 --> 00:41:06,996
YEAH. GET HER ON THE PHONE.
I WANT TO TALK TO HER.
I'M ACTUALLY THE ONE WHO WEARS
THE PANTS IN THE FAMILY,

00:41:06,996 --> 00:41:09,765
AND SHE'LL TELL YOU THAT.
I GET THAT, BUT I'M NOT‐‐
I'M NOT SURE‐‐

00:41:09,765 --> 00:41:12,435
YOU SEE HOW
HE'S INSULTING YOU ALREADY?

00:41:12,435 --> 00:41:14,704
JUST PULL THE CORD
ON THESE TWO GUYS.

00:41:14,704 --> 00:41:18,541
SHANE, I THINK YOU NEED TO MAKE
A DECISION RIGHT NOW.
YOU KNOW...

00:41:18,541 --> 00:41:21,077
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA SAY
DIFFERENT TO MY WIFE?

00:41:21,077 --> 00:41:23,079
LET'S‐‐I WANT TO TALK TO HER.
WELL...

00:41:23,079 --> 00:41:25,314
LET'S TALK TO HER.
YOU KNOW, TALK IS CHEAP.

00:41:25,314 --> 00:41:28,351
THAT'S THE BEAUTIFUL THING
ABOUT IT. LET'S TALK.
(Daymond) SHANE, LISTEN.
I'M STARTING...

00:41:28,351 --> 00:41:31,687
WE HAVE ANOTHER MINUTE. SHANE,
LET'S HAVE A MINUTE. SILENCE.
ONE SECOND, KEVIN.
I'M STARTING TO RECONSIDER.

00:41:31,687 --> 00:41:34,156
I‐I MAY RECONSIDER THE OFFER.
YOU KNOW WHY HE'S WORRIED?

00:41:34,156 --> 00:41:37,193
BECAUSE IN THE BACK
OF YOUR MIND, SEAN...
AND SCRAPE HIM OFF OF THAT THING
RIGHT THERE RIGHT NOW.

00:41:37,193 --> 00:41:39,362
YOU KNOW THAT THERE'S
SOMETHING HERE. YOU KNOW THERE'S

00:41:39,362 --> 00:41:41,697
SOMETHING HERE IN THIS LICENSE
DEAL YOU SHOULD CONSIDER.

00:41:41,697 --> 00:41:43,866
IT'S A MUCH BIGGER VISION,
YOU BECOME MUCH WEALTHIER,

00:41:43,866 --> 00:41:47,370
AND IT HAPPENS FASTER.
KEVIN, YOU'RE REALLY
EMBARRASSING YOURSELF RIGHT NOW.

00:41:47,370 --> 00:41:51,507
STAY HERE. I'LL BE BACK
TO YOU IN A MINUTE.
HE WALKS OUT, I'M WITHDRAWING.

00:41:51,507 --> 00:41:54,243
(Robert) SHANE, BE A MAN,
FOR GODS SAKE.
OKAY, WELL, SURE.
I‐I'M NEGOTIATING, ROBERT.

00:41:54,243 --> 00:41:56,946
I MEAN, THAT'S WHAT
I FEEL LIKE I'M DOING.

00:41:56,946 --> 00:42:00,383
I'M TRYING TO FIND WHAT'S BEST
FOR MY FAMILY AND FOR ME, SO...
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT HIM, BUT I'VE
JUST REDUCED MY $40,000 TO‐‐

00:42:00,383 --> 00:42:02,718
LISTEN. I'VE JUST REDUCED
MY $40,000 TO $30,000,

00:42:02,718 --> 00:42:04,987
SO NOW MY DEAL IS $70,000.

00:42:04,987 --> 00:42:08,424
I WOULD LIKE YOU TO RETAIN
THAT OFFER, AND I‐‐

00:42:08,424 --> 00:42:10,426
IF YOU WILL GO BACK
TO YOUR ORIGINAL OFFER,

00:42:10,426 --> 00:42:13,863
I'M GONNA‐‐I'M GONNA SAY
THAT I WANNA WORK WITH YOU.
RIGHT NOW?

00:42:13,863 --> 00:42:15,464
YES.
(O'Leary) ALL RIGHT.

00:42:15,464 --> 00:42:18,568
NOW I'M IN FOR THE $80,000
WITH YOU, DAYMOND.

00:42:20,469 --> 00:42:23,372
RIGHT‐‐I'M GONNA‐‐
LET'S DO IT RIGHT NOW. DEAL.

00:42:23,372 --> 00:42:26,742
ALL RIGHT. OKAY.
GOOD JOB.
(Barbara) GOOD DECISION.

00:42:26,742 --> 00:42:29,612
THANK YOU, MAN.
(Shane) I KNEW YOU WERE THE MAN.

00:42:29,612 --> 00:42:32,615
ALL RIGHT. OKAY.
ALL RIGHT.

00:42:32,615 --> 00:42:35,184
DEAD MAN SWEEPING.
(laughs)

00:42:35,184 --> 00:42:39,689
MAYBE WE LET THEM HAVE CANADA.
NO, WE'LL SEND 'EM SOME BROOMS.
WE'LL SEND 'EM SOME BROOMS.

00:42:39,689 --> 00:42:42,692
TO HAVE THEM BE THAT EXCITED
ABOUT MY PRODUCT, IT FELT GOOD,

00:42:42,692 --> 00:42:45,695
AND I'LL‐‐IT'LL ALLOW MY WIFE
TO STAY HOME WITH THE KIDS.

00:42:45,695 --> 00:42:48,631
SO FOR THAT, I AM
TRULY BLESSED AND EXCITED.

